639
00:45:31.732 --> 00:45:33.467
Yeah. it's okay.

640
00:45:46.013 --> 00:45:47.848
I think we should rest that leg.

641
00:45:48.583 --> 00:45:49.850
I can keep going.

642
00:45:50.017 --> 00:45:51.118
If we don't rest.

643
00:45:51.218 --> 00:45:52.753
