more vulnerable.

644
00:46:01.161 --> 00:46:03.364
Let's check out
this spot. It looks good.

645
00:46:03.797 --> 00:46:05.232
All right. let me
take a quick look.

646
00:46:05.332 --> 00:46:06.333
Okay.

647
00:46:17.579 --> 00:46:18.946
Nice.

648
00:46:21.348 --> 00:46:22.449
