and I tried to fight.

778
01:00:00.334 --> 01:00:01.570
And it didn't work. Okay?

779
01:00:01.635 --> 01:00:03.704
It just made things harder
and you don't want that.

780
01:00:03.871 --> 01:00:07.274
My advice...

781
01:00:07.942 --> 01:00:10.144
